    <date day="29" month="April" year="1997"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This memo describes Version 1.5 of the client/server interaction of RWhois.  RWhois provides a distributed system for the discovery, retrieval, and maintenance of directory information.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.
	 </t>
